  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "kicker",
      "content": "SPECIMEN BLUEPRINT  \u00b7  ACTOR-BASED SPATIAL SIMULATION ENGINE"
    },
    {
      "type": "pageTitle",
      "content": "Measured in Points"
    },
    {
      "type": "story",
      "content": "",
      "columns": 3,
      "gutter": 12,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "body",
          "content": "Every element arrived through collision \u2014 geometry negotiated in a single deterministic pass. Each block, glyph, and inline span is an actor reporting its own origin and extent. No iterative reflow; the engine converges in one traversal. Box positions are committed in that forward sweep; no downstream process revisits what the simulation resolved. Given the same document AST and the same fonts, every build produces identical output.",
          "properties": {
            "sourceId": "para-dropcap",
            "dropCap": {
              "enabled": true,
              "lines": 3,
              "gap": 5,
              "characterStyle": {
                "fontFamily": "Tinos",
                "fontWeight": 700,
                "color": "#7a3a52"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "obstacleImg",
          "content": "",
          "properties": {
            "sourceId": "obstacle-float",
            "image": {
              "data": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAIAAACQd1PeAAAADElEQVR42mP48OQMAAVoAqEPT7KoAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC",
              "mimeType": "image/png",
              "fit": "fill"
            },
            "style": { "width": 78, "height": 50 },
            "layout": { "mode": "float", "align": "left", "wrap": "around", "gap": 10 }
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "body",
          "content": "",
          "properties": { "sourceId": "para-2" },
          "children": [
            { "type": "text", "content": "Text reflows around every obstacle in one pass \u2014 no " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "iteration", "properties": { "style": { "fontStyle": "italic" } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": ", no backtracking. The float registers an exclusion field of " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "88 pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " (obstacle " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "78 pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " + gap " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "10 pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": "). Lines return to full " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "198 pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " column measure after the obstacle \u2014 " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "no renegotiation.", "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 700 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " The exclusion geometry is resolved before line-breaking begins; each line receives only its available width, not raw float geometry. Justified text adjusts to the narrowed measure beside the float and to the full measure below, in a single forward pass with no re-entry." }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "body",
          "content": "",
          "children": [
            { "type": "text", "content": "Margins", "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 700 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " are declared, not " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "negotiated", "properties": { "style": { "fontStyle": "italic" } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": ": " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "top 34", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": ", " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "right 50", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": ", " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "bottom 34", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": ", " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "left 50", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": ". No browser margin collapse, no sub-pixel drift. Identical geometry on every build. Adjacent margins never coalesce; block spacing is the exact sum of each element's declared properties \u2014 nothing more, nothing less." }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "body",
          "content": "",
          "children": [
            { "type": "text", "content": "Vertical metrics are read directly from the binary font file: ascent and descent from the " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "OS/2", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " table, advance widths from the " },
            { "type": "text", "content": "hmtx", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Cousine", "fontSize": 8.2, "backgroundColor": "#ecdfc8", "color": "#4a2c0a", "paddingLeft": 2, "paddingRight": 2 } } },
            { "type": "text", "content": " table. The baseline coordinate is derived from font-reported values, not averaged from the em-square. Sub-pixel accuracy is preserved at every stage." }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "body",
          "content": "Column flow is depth-first: the left column fills to its declared height before text continues in the next. Orphan and widow controls prevent isolated lines at column edges; the minimum threshold is two. Hyphenation fires automatically beyond the minimum word length using language-aware exception tables.",
          "properties": {}
        }
      ]
    },
